metadata.name: VenIstanbul
metadata.description: Robin, who was born and raised in Istanbul and later move to Italy, brought these two cultures together with his VenIstanbul work. He reinterpreted the characteristic streets of Balat (IST) and Venice (IT) with his point of view. As an artist who knows the Eastern and Western cultures closely, this situation was reflected in his work. The main purpose of this work is creating smile on people's face. This work was sponsored by Acer Turkey.
